data.description: Beautifully updated home in central Tucson near Randolf Park and Davis Monthan AFB. Open kitchen with grand island and ample supply of new cabinetswith granite countertops. Flooring featuring ceramic tile and carpet. Two living spaces are a family living room complete with antique wood burning stoveand formal living room off the kitchen. New AC, new dual pane windows and new upgraded electrical panel. Large north facing back yard. Three storage shedsand plenty of parking. Low care landscaping front and back and an easy commute to downtown and U of A. Property also features updated gas line service;repaired sewer main connection; and re-coated roof.
